Recap - Pods kubernetes 

--Container directly does not deploy in worker node

    "for that require Pods"

--Pods is sible object in kubernetes


--------------

Create Multiple Pod inside Single node
        use bellow command to create multiple Pods(For 3 pods)

     Docker run python-app

     Docker run python-app

     Docker run python-app   

 and link  command

    Docker run helper -link app1

    Docker run helper -link app2
    
    Docker run helper -link app3





 Kubectl
 Nginx install in node -------------

    Kubectl run nginx --image nginx
    
---> List of pods 

    kubectl get pods